episodes.title: Smoke Signals
episodes.plot: David scouts a potential wedding venue, while Johnny and Moira have a romantic picnic by the creek.

episodes.title: The Incident
episodes.plot: David is embarrassed by a childhood issue that resurfaces, and only spirals further when Patrick is so understanding; Johnny, Stevie and Roland attend a viewing for a nearby motel; Alexis helps Moira join social media.

episodes.title: The Job Interview
episodes.plot: Johnny and Moira endeavor to secure an investor for a new motel while, Alexis and Ted struggle with long distance.

episodes.title: Maid of Honour
episodes.plot: Moira shares the newly released Crows movie trailer with the Jazzagals. Johnny and Roland find a suspicious bag of money at the new motel.

episodes.title: The Premiere
episodes.plot: Alexis plans a local premiere for the "Crows" movie, and Moira makes a big splash on the red carpet; David tends to Patrick after his wisdom teeth removal.

episodes.title: The Wingman
episodes.plot: Alexis and Moira deal with the aftermath of a viral video, while Johnny helps Bob get back out in the dating world.

episodes.title: Moira Rosé
episodes.plot: Moira and David sample wine at Herb Ertlinger's vineyard, while Johnny attempts to have "the talk" with Patrick.

episodes.title: The Presidential Suite
episodes.plot: Johnny and Moira spend a night at the presidential suite in the new motel, while Alexis receives a surprise visitor.

episodes.title: Rebound
episodes.plot: Johnny becomes overly involved in Alexis's romantic life, while Moira offends the townspeople in an interview with People magazine.

episodes.title: Sunrise, Sunset
episodes.plot: Moira's former "Sunrise Bay" producers show up with big news while Alexis binge-watches old episodes of the soap.

episodes.title: The Bachelor Party
episodes.plot: The Roses attend the "Escape Room" portion of David and Patrick's Bachelor Party, but their participation wanes the more their personal dilemmas come to a head.

episodes.title: The Pitch
episodes.plot: Johnny, Stevie and Roland head to New York for their pitch meeting, and the family anxiously awaits their return.

episodes.title: Start Spreading the News
episodes.plot: Moira receives some unexpected news, and David makes a tough decision about where he wants to live.

episodes.title: Happy Ending
episodes.plot: David stresses out over the rain on his wedding day, but his family makes it right.
